<script type="text/javascript">
function togPhase(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + n);
	e.style.display = e.style.display == 'none' ? 'block' : 'none';
}
function togAllPhases(display) {
	for (var i = 1; i <= 50; i++) {
		var e = document.getElementById('phasehint' + i);
		if (!e) break;
		e.style.display = display;
	}
}
function addHint(n) {
	var e = document.getElementById('phase');
	for (var i = 0; i < e.childNodes.length; i++) {
		e.childNodes[i].selected = e.childNodes[i].value == n ? 'selected' : '';
	}
	e = document.getElementById('text');
	e.focus();
	e.select();
}
</script>

<div class="mm white">
This quest <span class="blue">[<span class="yellow">2166</span>]</span> is called '<span class="yellow">Galloping Gargoyles</span>',<br/>
for Adventurers levels <span class="yellow">120</span> to <span class="yellow">240</span>.<br />


<span class="hg"><a href="/npc/3438">Lord Vashir</a> [<a href="/area/61">The Towne of New Rigel</a>] is the master in charge of this quest.</span><br />

The other day, my daughter told me that she had recently developed an<br />
interest in gargoyles.  My daughter has to always get what she wants, and<br />
that is why I'm assigning you this task.  Find yourself a decent mount, a<br />
pegasus will do, and run to nearby towns in search of gargoyles for my<br />
daughter.  Some towns that I suggest are Rune, and Diocletian.  Please hurry<br />
back, as my daughter is already expressing an urge to have gargoyles right<br />
now.  Be quick and you will receive an ample reward for your efforts.<br />

<span class="hy">Upon successful completion of this quest you can receive:</span><br />

<span class="hm">*</span>Up to <span class="yellow">50</span> quest points, <span class="yellow">4</span> practice points, <span class="yellow">15,000</span> experience points,<br/>
&nbsp;<span class="yellow">0</span> build points, <span class="yellow">0</span> piety, and <span class="yellow">12,000</span> gold pieces.<br />


You have <span class="yellow">250</span> minutes remaining to complete this quest.<br />

Galloping Gargoyles consists of:<br />


	<div class="phase" id="phase1">


		<a class="hints" href="javascript:togPhase(1);">Phase 1</a>: Rescue <a href="/npc/1653">A young pegasus</a>. 		
		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint1" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinfomob">in <a href="/area/1">Alyria</a>.</div>


