		<div class="phasehints" id="phasehint2" style="display: none;">

<div class="phaseinfomob">in <a href="/area/67">Towne of Rune</a>.</div>


			<div class="phasehint">
				Above rune temple, lever to the locked door is at the entrance to the rune crypts				&mdash;
				Drean							</div>


		</div>
	</div>


